<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/output.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/index.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/menu.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css"
    integrity="sha512-Evv84Mr4kqVGRNSgIGL/F/aIDqQb7xQ2vcrdIwxfjThSH8CSR7PBEakCr51Ck+w+/U6swU2Im1vVX0SVk9ABhg=="
    crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
  <title>XV Maria</title>
</head>

<body class="bg-pastel-claro font-dancing">

  <!-- Contenedor para la lluvia de sobres -->


  <!-- mensaje -->
  <section id="seccion-mensaje"
    class="fixed text-center  h-screen w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center top-0 opacity-0 p-5">
    <article class=" w-full sm:w-3/4  flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
      <p class=" text-center max-w-xl font-dancing text-3xl text-gray-800 font-light translate-y-10"><span
          class="font-bold">En mi corazón
          siempre hubo un sueño...</span><br>
        Me soñaba vestida de princesa, como en un cuento de hadas.
        Hoy, al cumplir mis 15 y hermosos años,
        dejo atrás mi adorada infancia,
        que junto a los míos la pase muy feliz. <br><br>
        <span class="font-medium">
          Hoy mi sueño se hace realidad...
        </span>
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <div id="inicio-mask"
    class="transition-opacity  pointer-events-none z-10 opacity-100 bg-verde-claro fixed top-0 w-full h-screen ">
    <section class="">
      <picture id="picture-inicio" class="h-screen w-full scale-125 block overflow-hidden fixed">
        <img src="/assets/img/fondoPrueba.jpg" alt="" class="absolute h-full w-full object-cover">
        <img src="/assets/img/maria.png" alt=""
          class="img15 absolute h-full object-cover mx-auto left-0 right-0 animate-duration-500  animate-blurred-fade-in">
        <img src="/assets/img/logo-maria.png" alt="" id="maria-logo"
          class="absolute w-full scale-105 translate-y-15 min-w-2xs  mx-auto left-0 right-0 object-cover  sm:h-full sm:w-auto sm:translate-0 sm:scale-100 ">
        <img src="/assets/img/mitadDerecha.png" alt=""
          class="absolute h-full object-cover mx-auto left-0 right-0 translate-x-5/12 animate-blurred-fade-in animate-duration-500 mask-b-from-20% mask-b-to-100%  mask-l-from-95% mask-l-to-100%">
      </picture>

      <!-- cuenta regresiva-->
      <footer class="w-full absolute bottom-0 m-auto p-10 flex justify-center ">
        <div id="clock" class=" left-0 right-0 m-auto flex justify-between w-auto gap-5 p-4 
                            bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md rounded-3xl shadow-xl">
          <!-- mariposa -->
          <div class="mariposa absolute top-0 left-0 -translate-x-6 fill-white rotate-35">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 18.528 35.424" version="1.1" y="0" x="0" height="369" width="193"
